components.content:
This section contains various software projects that I've built.

Since it does take some effort the to create project articles, I regret to say that I am unable to make the list exhaustive. Old projects for which it is too cumbersome to extract files and assets from old computers will be omitted. Proprietary intellectual property that belongs to myself, past clients, or employers will also not be included on my website. 

The array of projects spans multiple programming languages and features different technologies. From native Windows desktop application written in C++, to application server written in PHP. From front-end Javascript and CSS, to serverless backend code written in Python. There socket connection
